 He saw how tired she was and felt a little concerned.."I'll finish up here, 
I want you to get some sleep. You are no help to us tired. And I want you 
full alert when we plan our next move against Megatron..please do not refuse. 
Let me help." He wrote down the postion of her quarters on a piece of 
paper..."Now go and sleep." he handed her the paper.
